 * | | | `-- Patch Version Number.
 * | | |
 * | | `---- 0 = Alpha.
 * | |       1 = Beta.
 * | |       2 = RC.
 * | |       3 = Release.
 * | |
 * | `------ Minor Version Change.
 * |
 * `-------- Major Version Change.
 */
